item.title: CVE-2023-21442|2024-08-02T09:36:34.478Z -- samsung%20mobile -- runestone
item.description: Improper access control vulnerability in Runestone application prior to version 2.9.09.003 in Android R(11) and 3.2.01.007 in Android S(12) allows local attackers to get device location information.
